    },
    {
      "audio": 6,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "それで神様が怒ってしまい",
          "en": "And then the gods became angry."
        },
        {
          "ja": "彦星と引き離されたんだよね",
          "en": "He was separated from Hikoboshi, right?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 7,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "で　七夕っていうのは",
