    },
    {
      "audio": 14,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "それで　笹はいつ食べるの？",
          "en": "So, when do we eat the bamboo leaves?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "だから　食べないって",
          "en": "That's why we don't eat it."
        },
        {
          "ja": "紙なんかで作った飾りをいっぱいつけて",
          "en": "Attach lots of decorations made from paper and such."
        },
        {
          "ja": "それから　願いごとを書いた短冊なんかもぶら下げるんだよ",
          "en": "And then, we also hang up strips of paper with our wishes written on them."
        }
